{"word":"H4068 - מָדֹון - Mâdôwn - maw-dohn' - Madon","slug":"H4068","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָדֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Mâdôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-dohn'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Madon"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>מדון</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>mâdôn</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>maw-dohn'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Madon = \"strife\" <ol><li>one of the principal cities of Canaan who joined Jabin and his confederates in their battle against Joshua at the waters of Merom and were defeated</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H4067\">H4067</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1777\">H1777</a>, <a href=\"#/H1779\">H1779</a>, <a href=\"#/H1781\">H1781</a>, <a href=\"#/H1783\">H1783</a>, <a href=\"#/H1835\">H1835</a>, <a href=\"#/H1839\">H1839</a>, <a href=\"#/H1840\">H1840</a>, <a href=\"#/H1842\">H1842</a>, <a href=\"#/H3036\">H3036</a>, <a href=\"#/H4066\">H4066</a>, <a href=\"#/H4079\">H4079</a>, <a href=\"#/H4080\">H4080</a>, <a href=\"#/H4082\">H4082</a>, <a href=\"#/H4084\">H4084</a>, <a href=\"#/H4090\">H4090</a>, <a href=\"#/H4091\">H4091</a>, <a href=\"#/H4092\">H4092</a>, <a href=\"#/H7384\">H7384</a>"}]}